Each subdirectory is considered a subtest of test_verify_bundle
* the name of the directory is the subtest name
* name should end in "_fail" if the verification is expected to fail
* directory must contain
  * bundle.sigstore.json: The signature bundle
  * README: Explanation of the test: why it should fail/succeed
* directory may contain
  * artifact: The signed artifact (if not provided, "a.txt" from the top
    level dir is used)
  * trusted_root.json: a custom trusted root (if one is not provided,
    current production instance trusted root is used)
